This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with visual SLAM and dense reconstruction. The use of optical flow also suggests that it may belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as optical flow is commonly used in robot navigation. The paper also involves segmentation and classification, which are topics commonly found in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper may also belong to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as it deals with 3D reconstruction.
